{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_23051.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810600,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day11_s.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bgm":"bgm01_anime03","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":810600,"pos":0}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Good morning, Hitomi!"},{"chara":[{"id":810600,"motion":100}],"nameAvLeft":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Good morning."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":810600}],"nameAvLeft":"Hitomi","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...Oh?@Miss Akemi is with you?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200301,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]G-good morning."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":100,"pos":2},{"id":810600,"motion":1}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]We ended up walking home@together yesterday."},{"chara":[{"id":200101}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So I invited her to come along@with us in the morning."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200301,"motion":100,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]S-sorry, I didn't mean to suddenly impose..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810600,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]There's no need to apologize."},{"chara":[{"id":810600}],"nameAvLeft":"Hitomi","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I'd love to get to know more about you."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200301,"motion":200}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]O-oh, of course!"},{"bgmFadeOut":3000,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":810600,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameAvLeft":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]By the way, Madoka..."},{"chara":[{"id":810600}],"nameAvLeft":"Hitomi","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Have you heard anything from Sayaka?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":201,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]No... Not that I know of.@Is something wrong?"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime04","chara":[{"id":810600,"motion":100}],"nameAvLeft":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Last night, we got a call@from Sayaka's mother."},{"chara":[{"id":810600}],"nameAvLeft":"Hitomi","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Apparently she hasn't come home,@so they're asking around for information."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Wha...?!@Sayaka is missing?"},{"chara":[{"id":810600,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]When we parted ways,@she mentioned going to look at CDs..."},{"chara":[{"id":810600,"motion":300}],"nameAvLeft":"Hitomi","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]After that, there was a robbery@at the shopping mall."},{"chara":[{"id":810600}],"nameAvLeft":"Hitomi","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So I'm worried something might@have happened to her..."},{"chara":[{"id":200101,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]O-oh, I see..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200301,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Um, is Sayaka...a mutual friend of yours?"},{"chara":[{"id":200101}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Mhm. We usually all hang out together,@but..."},{"chara":[{"id":200101,"motion":300}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I wonder what happened..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
